Hobo:
Hobos may build on sidewalks only, not touching other players' property.
Hobos cannot own doors or base with other players.
Hobos cannot intentionally block the view of players' bases.
Hobos may beg for money but cannot mug or raid.

Thief:
Only Thieves & Swat may raid.
Max 3 raiders per group. Anyone not in your group may be killed or asked to leave during a raid.
You must click the raid button on the property to start and end a raid.
You must make an effort to steal during a raid. No killing and leaving without taking anything.
15 minute cooldown before raiding the same base again.
Code raiding is allowed.

Hitman: 
Only kill your assigned target
Hitmen with an active hit displayed are KOS
Do no accept hits on the same person repeatedly.

Police/Swat:
NO RDA. Only arrest players with VALID REASON.
Must have a valid reason to raid.
Cannot own printers or illegal items.
Cannot base with criminals.
CANNOT LOCK THE STATION DOWN FOR NO REASON.

Gun Dealer/Black Market Dealer:
Cannot self-supply and switch jobs.
May own a shop but cannot raid or mug.

Medic:
Must heal all players who request it.
Cannot participate in raids or criminal activity.
May charge for healing services.

Meth Maker:
May only produce and sell meth, no raiding or mugging.
Must base to cook meth.
Can defend your meth lab if raided.
May hire security

as this game mode is still WIP, rules aren't fully established yet, just don't be a dumbass, if staff thinks something breaks common sense, it's their final word.

